Avery Inc said it began a publicoffering of two mln shars at 50.25 dlrs per shares.    PUrchasers of the shares are entitled to get one additionalshare for each share purchased to give effect to thetwo-for-one stock split approved by the board February 26.    There are about 19.9 mln shares outstanding on a presplitbasis, it said.    Proceeds will be used to reduce borrowings and othergeneral purposes. Reuter&#3;